featured real-time chat application built with Spring Boot (Kotlin) and Vue 3 (TypeScript). It supports user authentication, private/group messaging, typing indicators, and WebRTC audio calls.",[25,161,36],{"id":35},[163,164,166],"h3",{"id":165},"backend","Backend",[38,168,169,175,181,187,193],{},[41,170,171,174],{},[44,172,173],{},"Authentication",": JWT-based login/registration.",[41,176,177,180],{},[44,178,179],{},"Real-time Messaging",": WebSocket (STOMP) for instant message delivery.",[41,182,183,186],{},[44,184,185],{},"WebRTC Signaling",": Handling call offers, answers, and ICE candidates.",[41,188,189,192],{},[44,190,191],{},"Persistence",": PostgreSQL database with JPA/Hibernate.",[41,194,195,198],{},[44,196,197],{},"Security",": Spring Security + JWT.",[163,200,202],{"id":201},"frontend","Frontend",[38,204,205,211,217,223],{},[41,206,207,210],{},[44,208,209],{},"Modern UI",": Built with Nuxt UI and Tailwind CSS.",[41,212,213,216],{},[44,214,215],{},"State Management",": Pinia for reactive data handling.",[41,218,219,222],{},[44,220,221],{},"Real-time Updates",": Live chat updates and typing status.",[41,224,225,228],{},[44,226,227],{},"Voice Calls",": WebRTC integration for peer-to-peer audio calls.",{"title":97,"searchDepth":98,"depth":98,"links":230},[231],{"id":35,"depth":98,"text":36,"children":232},[233,235],{"id":165,"depth":234,"text":166},3,{"id":201,"depth":234,"text":202},"https://image2url.com/r2/default/images/1774865798254-12aa3de8-c066-4997-bfe9-d658e97bd842.png","Full featured Chat app with voice and video calls feature","https://github.com/kratosgado/chatapp",[240,241,236,242,243,244],"https://image2url.com/r2/default/images/1774865732629-481c876e-b06a-4229-90ba-81773d46eae5.png","https://image2url.com/r2/default/images/1774865773848-b44133e1-5d0f-42eb-8942-4aa16ee1e24d.png","https://image2url.com/r2/default/images/1774865832196-e0c7d7bd-a04d-46a3-93ad-167f34246fdf.png","https://image2url.com/r2/default/images/1774865863500-446f5e3a-8568-4f